    "# pix2pix-zero — Colab Inference Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook is prepared for a GitHub repository and can be opened directly in Google Colab.\n",
    "\n",
    "**What it does**\n",
    "- Clones the official pix2pix-zero repository.\n",
    "- Installs dependencies for a current Colab environment.\n",
    "- Applies compatibility patches for newer Diffusers and Transformers versions.\n",
    "- Lets you upload custom images and choose predefined editing tasks.\n",
    "- Runs inversion, editing, visualization, and experiment logging.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Recommended runtime:** Google Colab with GPU enabled.\n",
    "\n",
    "**How to use**\n",
    "1. Open the notebook in Colab.\n",
    "2. Run the setup and patching cells.\n",
    "3. Upload your input images.\n",
    "4. Select an experiment from the case library.\n",
    "5. Run inversion, editing, display, and logging cells.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
